Detailed Description

Struct hold info about the file format for mesh.

Description:

Need to keep offset to topology and global IDs.

NOTE: We also keep the mesh's part or material ID, but this is stored up a level on the mesh's fileInfo object so that it can be retained when writing to a different file.

Modifications:

  • 7/18/2005 WSD Created.
